2024-10-08 18:45:22 INFO tmdb.py - {'page': 1, 'results': [{'adult': False, 'backdrop_path': '/2mu6XkJE0B6nK5jeOvXOyWPVmhw.jpg', 'genre_ids': [35, 18, 10749], 'id': 401, 'original_language': 'en', 'original_title': 'Garden State', 'overview': 'Andrew Largeman (Braff) vuelve a su casa natal, en Nueva Jersey, después de diez años de ausencia para asistir al funeral de su madre. Allí rememora su pasado y conoce a una chica, Samantha (Portman), que quizá pueda cambiar su vida. Largeman, que acaba de dejar los antidepresivos que ha estado tomando durante años, comienza a redescubrirse a sí mismo, lo que incluye enfrentarse a su padre, psicólogo, y ayudar a Samantha a superar sus propios problemas pisicológicos.', 'popularity': 11.739, 'poster_path': '/g3BYRs7EzzTvUaGfbyYSwxhNI7A.jpg', 'release_date': '2004-07-28', 'title': 'Algo en común', 'video': False, 'vote_average': 7.084, 'vote_count': 1807}, {'adult': False, 'backdrop_path': None, 'genre_ids': [], 'id': 1295069, 'original_language': 'en', 'original_title': 'Garden State', 'overview': 'Filmed in various locations throughout New Jersey, Garden State explores the diverse landscapes in which wildlife, development, farming, and industry coexist in the most densely packed state in the union. Thematically concerned with utopian/dystopian ideas about modernist ‘progress’, the static camera lens observes New Jersey without judgement in order to allow the viewer to draw connections between the visual poetics of the landscape and the overwhelming legacy of human intervention. Kevin T. Allen’s sound design-- a heightened soundtrack of organically sourced hums and drones -- lures the viewer into a hypnotic and meditative experience while sonically announcing the presence of the human figure in the landscape. Garden State both encourages us to slow down, take a long lingering look at our surroundings, and to find wonder, beauty, ruin, and awe in the most unlikely of places.', 'popularity': 0.178, 'poster_path': None, 'release_date': '2024-05-30', 'title': 'Garden State', 'video': False, 'vote_average': 0.0, 'vote_count': 0}, {'adult': False, 'backdrop_path': '/50tPHgHeWxyHYFKUQOEhoYMJjls.jpg', 'genre_ids': [], 'id': 1011784, 'original_language': 'en', 'original_title': 'Garden State Pro Wrestling: Welcome To Eden', 'overview': 'On July 23rd Garden State Pro Wrestling debuts live with "Welcome To Eden" straight from The Heart Ballroom in Newark, New Jersey!  The event is double headlined by two huge main events. In both matches the contenders are stepping in the ring against each other for the first time ever - they are Josh Alexander vs Konosuke Takeshita and Taya Valkyrie vs Trish Adora.  The event features and the Openweight Championship 8 wrestler tournament. The first round matchups are already announced, check them below:  Davey Richards vs Robert Martyr, Kevin Blackwood vs Alan "5" Angels, Effy vs Bryan Keith & Tony Deppen vs Calvin Tankman. Other matches on the show include Miyu Yamashita vs Billie Starkz vs Janai Kai, Dark Sheik & Jai Vidal vs Edith Surreal & Heather Monroe and YDNB (Jordan Oliver, Charlie Tiger, Griffin McCoy) vs TEAM H20 (Marcus Mathers, Reid Walker, Austin Luke).', 'popularity': 0.039, 'poster_path': '/mdiqVXA0nLVzbnIXQjxqjejY2JT.jpg', 'release_date': '2022-07-23', 'title': 'Garden State Pro Wrestling: Welcome To Eden', 'video': False, 'vote_average': 0.0, 'vote_count': 0}, {'adult': False, 'backdrop_path': None, 'genre_ids': [10402, 99], 'id': 324409, 'original_language': 'en', 'original_title': 'The Marshall Tucker Band - Live From The Garden State 1981', 'overview': 'In 1981, The Marshall Tucker Band filmed a live concert for broadcast on MTV. All original members performed except for Tommy Caldwell, who died in a car crash in 1980. The footage is a document to be treasured, capturing as it does a defining moment in the band’s history – on the heels of tragedy, but at the top of their musical game.\r Also included is the documentary called "Which One Is Marshall Tucker?".', 'popularity': 0.001, 'poster_path': '/aWZVwEzW4QvH2vLppUcZR09G6qg.jpg', 'release_date': '2004-11-01', 'title': 'The Marshall Tucker Band - Live From The Garden State 1981', 'video': False, 'vote_average': 0.0, 'vote_count': 0}], 'total_pages': 1, 'total_results': 4}
