ert', 'video': False, 'vote_average': 6.0, 'vote_count': 1}, {'adult': False, 'backdrop_path': '/vf8ytUMl9pZITkqAyyV7UnR5Dye.jpg', 'genre_ids': [10402], 'id': 1109418, 'original_language': 'en', 'original_title': 'Alfie Boe - Bring Him Home Tour Live', 'overview': 'Filmed live at the Royal Festival Hall in London, during Alfie Boers sell out tour; the star of Les Misérables and the much loved tenor showcases his mesmerising and outstanding voice in his very own  show \'Bring Him Home\'. With an impressively diverse collection of tracks including the impassioned "Maria" from West Side Story, Ewan MacColl\'s heartfelt "The First Time Ever I Saw Your Face", a truly breathtaking rendition of "Bring Him Home" from Les Misérables and an emotional performance of Martina McBride\'s \'In My Daughters Eyes\'. Plus, Alfie performs a wonderful medley of James Bond theme tunes, and uniquely inspired renditions of tune: from Moulin Rouge, Chitty Chitty Bang Bang and much more. Alfie is also joined on stage for some unique performances by his very special guests, including Matt Lucas, Melanie C, Tom Fletcher from McFly Claude-Michel Schönberg and Shakira Riddell-Morales.', 'popularity': 0.351, 'poster_path': '/eT70kUX5DgzvMTTFxtIvXn6manb.jpg', 'release_date': '2011-10-01', 'title': 'Alfie Boe - Bring Him Home Tour Live', 'video': False, 'vote_average': 0.0, 'vote_count': 0}, {'adult': False, 'backdrop_path': None, 'genre_ids': [12], 'id': 948144, 'original_language': 'en', 'original_title': "Alfie and Gully's Holy Chalice Quest", 'overview': "To save their mother from a wizard's curse, two siblings must go on a quest for a chalice that heal all ailments.", 'popularity': 0.091, 'poster_path': '/8QphwoofJa6IfxiILEwKjmTkeaT.jpg', 'release_date': '2022-05-15', 'title': "Alfie and Gully's Holy Chalice Quest", 'video': False, 'vote_average': 10.0, 'vote_count': 1}, {'adult': False, 'backdrop_path': None, 'genre_ids': [10402], 'id': 1081890, 'original_language': 'en', 'original_title': '